description: Ordered wrong mount for your LCD? No problem, use this wall mount adapter with mounts that didn't match the mount pattern on your display. Your TV mount hole pattern may exceed the size of TV plate of your mount. This universal wall mount extender/adapter extends all standard and non standard 200x200 or large mounting hole pattern. VESA extension adapter kit can increase the support whole pattern up to 200mm total. This set includes 4 adapter plates, each extends 50mm or 100 mm. It has been tested to hold over 180 lb. However the actual loading capacity is limited by the wall mount too. Please check the loading capacity of your wall mount before you apply this adapter.
title: VideoSecu VESA Adapter Plate LED LCD Plasma TV Wall Mount Bracket Extender MLEB 1UU
